{% extends 'layouts/base.njk' %}

{% block head_title_content %}Register with a GP - NHS.UK{% endblock %}

{% block body_main_content %}

  {% block header_section %}
    <div class="local-header">
      <h1 class="local-header__title">{% block header_section_title %} Help us improve <br>Register with a GP {% endblock %}</h1>
    </div>
  {% endblock %}

  <div class="page-section">
    <div class="reading-width signup-survey">
      <p> We're improving the way people register with their GP.</p>
      <p> We're building an online services to do this that's:
      <ul>
        <li>secure</li>
         <li>free for patients and GP practices</li>
         <li>mirros current GMS1 and New Patient information forms</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="sub-header signup-subheader">Please take a quick (5 min) survey to:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>tell us about your registration process</li>
        <li>tell us if you want to try the service</li>
      </ul>

      <a href="" class="button start-step-btn" id="start-button">Start survey</a>

      <h3 class="sub-header signup-subheader">How the service works</h3>

      <h3 class="sub-header signup-subheader">In summary</h3>
      <p>Patients provide the same registration details as the GMS1 and most new
        patient information forms (like medical history, allergies etc).</p>

      <p> Patient details sent safely and securely to your preferred nhs.net email.</p>

      <p> If needed, patients told to provide proof of ID and addressin person at your surgery.</p>

      <p> The service is: </p>
      <ul>
        <li>safe and secure</li>
        <li>free and easy to use</li>
        <li>works on desktops, mobiles and tablets</li>
        <li>ensures patients provides correct information (like NHS number, address etc)
      </ul>

      <a href="{{ firstStep }}" class="button start-step-btn" id="start-button">Start survey</a>
    </div>
    
    <form method="post" id="current-step-form" action="#googleformlink">
      {% block submitRow %}
        <div class="form-group continue-step">
          <button type="submit" class="button">Form</button>
        </div>
      {% endblock submitRow %}

    </form>
  </div>
{% endblock body_main_content %}
